author: skitching
msg: Simplify discovery by using table of classes to check. Also enhance diagnostics a little.
There are no functional changes in this patch.

author: andreas
msg: Delete temp cocoon.xconf patch file on exit. This avoids that the build cancels under Windows when a file locking error occurs. The temp file won't be deleted in this case, so there's still room for improvement.
Bug: http://issues.apache.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=35394, Patch supplied by Jan Metzner. Thanks!
